s their focus Deleuze's philosophical relationship to classical pragmatism and the work of Peirce, James and Dewey.  a4410aDeleuze, Gilles,d1925-1995. 0aPragmatism.1 aBowden, Sean.1 aPatton, Paul. 0aRoutledge studies in contemporary philosophy.403University of Alberta Accessuhttp://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?direct=true&scope=site&db=nlebk&db=nlabk&AN=849948z(Single User Access)  aInternet AccesshUAINzPDAOWNED  aInternet AccesswLCc1i6773209-1001lINTERNETmUAINTERNETrYsYtE-RESOURCEu1/12/2015xE-BOOKzPDAOWNED01bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/113322838